{"author":"Joe Oakhart","data":{"alias":"tight-wasp-name","description":"# Decompose transition_compute (237-LOC / 10-param orchestrator)\n\n## What\n`_commands/transition.py:329-565` inlines plan-review gate, parent cascade, open-children guard, completion precheck, signing, force-close audit, compact+scratch+push. Extract `_close_ticket(...)` (the close-path tail) and `_cascade_open_parent(...)` (mirroring claim_compute), keeping `transition_compute` a ~80-LOC ordered sequencer. Preserve the verify->close->sign ordering invariant.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] `_close_ticket` + `_cascade_open_parent` extracted; `transition_compute` is a thin sequencer.\n- [ ] The ordering invariant + all transition/close/cascade tests pass unchanged.\n- [ ] `make lint` passes; commit carries a `rebar-ticket:` trailer.","id":"3777-1a90-694a-4aba","parent_id":"9322-f84a-e047-4471","priority":1,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"task","title":"Decompose transition_compute (237-LOC / 10-param orchestrator)"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1783056811142108001,"uuid":"4e4c250d-64de-4d4c-9fb1-d48a7d596d24"}